# Team Availability Tracker 👥

A Flask-based dashboard application that displays team members and their availability status. Users can toggle between AVAILABLE and BUSY states, and changes are stored in a SQLite database.

---

## 🚀 Features

- View team members
- Toggle availability status
- Real-time UI updates
- SQLite database integration
- Conditional rendering using Flask

---

## 🛠️ Technologies Used

- Python
- Flask
- SQLite
- HTML
- CSS

